				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Fred Anderson, Crucible of War: The Seven Years&#8217; War and the Fate of Empire in British North America, 1754-1766.  The Rev War was a direct extension of the 7YW (1754-1763), which was itself a continuation of King George&#8217;s War (1740-1748).  So, there is at least a twenty year period pre-1775 of scholarship ripe for further inclusion.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

