				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>PICTORIAL FIELD BOOK OF THE REVOLUTION, in 2 volumes, by BENSON J. LOSSING. 1850.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-99379' data-commentid="99379" data-postid="13549" data-belowelement="div-comment-99379" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Matthew von Hobe" aria-label='Reply to Matthew von Hobe'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
