				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Jane,<br />
If you want a raw, blow-by-blow daily account from an important primary source, then I would suggest starting with the Journals of Each Provincial Congress of Massachusetts in 1774 and 1775:  <a href="https://archive.org/details/journalsofeachprma00mass" rel="nofollow ugc">https://archive.org/details/journalsofeachprma00mass</a></p>
