					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://allthingsliberty.com/2017/03/100-best-american-revolution-books-time/#comment-100027"><time datetime="2017-03-16T16:15:29-04:00">March 16, 2017 at 4:15 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

