			<article id="div-comment-133647" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2de9c3362caf13d20181d7a2f7d9d0b?s=32&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2de9c3362caf13d20181d7a2f7d9d0b?s=64&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/>						<b class="fn">Donna M Miller</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://allthingsliberty.com/2017/03/100-best-american-revolution-books-time/#comment-133647"><time datetime="2020-05-07T12:06:08-04:00">May 7, 2020 at 12:06 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Revolutionary Brothers by Tom Chaffin. &#8220;Thomas Jefferson, the Marquis de Lafayette, and the Friendship that Helped Forge Two Nationa.&#8221;</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-133647' data-commentid="133647" data-postid="13549" data-belowelement="div-comment-133647" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Donna M Miller" aria-label='Reply to Donna M Miller'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li id="comment-135387" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">
			<article id="div-comment-135387" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f3f9b57e77bc4cb227101a3d9c6143c?s=32&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f3f9b57e77bc4cb227101a3d9c6143c?s=64&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/>						<b class="fn">Ron Mansfield</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

