						<a href="https://allthingsliberty.com/2017/03/100-best-american-revolution-books-time/#comment-135387"><time datetime="2020-07-09T19:00:37-04:00">July 9, 2020 at 7:00 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thank you for the excellent list. I would add another vote for Robert Middlekauff’s <em>The Glorious Cause</em>. Rick Atkinson&#8217;s <em>The British Are Coming</em> was also outstanding. I am really looking forward to his subsequent volumes. Glad to see Mark Lender&#8217;s and Garry Stone&#8217;s <em>Fatal Sunday</em> make the list, fantastic book.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

