				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>The Last King of America by Roberts is a recent bio in George III &amp; it&#8217;s an exceptional read. Not only is it a thorough understanding of who George was, but it explains the complicated politics of the period like no other book has done. Finished it yesterday, and cannot recommend it enough.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

